snippet.title: Super Mario RPG 100% Walkthrough - Part 8 [HD]
snippet.description:
Super Mario RPG: Legend of The Seven Stars Walkthrough - Part 8:

We enter more into the forest. We won frog coins by jumping several times on the Wigglers and We met one more chief of the Smithy gang called Bowyer who was throwing us arrows at Rose Town. And apparently he has our second star.

Visited Places:
Forest Maze

Level(s) Reached:
8

Star Pieces:
1
